ork out somehow.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eI give it an extra half star because I like how the end sort of wrapped up everything nicely, while at the same time leaving a little dangling question, and I like how the romance between Verity and Ned was handled in juxtaposition to the saccharine Tossie and St. Trewes thing. Oh, and I did like the part with Baine, and Tossie, and the river... \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eSo 2 stars overall... 2 1/2 for a satisfying conclusion... ","rating":2,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/1209800?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"historical-fiction","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/1209800?shelf=historical-fiction"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/55066856"},"likeCount":35,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":4,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Work:kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.shYzrp3-WNjQlw6xW93D4w":{"id":"kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.shYzrp3-WNjQlw6xW93D4w","__typename":"Work","legacyId":696,"bestBook":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.LV12moJFdGVn95fuzXP1zA"},"details":{"__typename":"WorkDetails","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/696-to-say-nothing-of-the-dog-or-how-we-found-the-bishop-s-bird-stump-at-la","shelvesUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/shelves/696-to-say-nothing-of-the-dog-or-how-we-found-the-bishop-s-bird-stump-at-la","publicationTime":883641600000,"originalTitle":"To Say Nothing of the Dog, or How We Found the Bishop's Bird Stump at Last","awardsWon":[{"__typename":"Award","name":"Hugo Award","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/award/show/9-hugo-award","awardedAt":915177600000,"category":"Best Novel","hasWon":true},{"__typename":"Award","name":"Nebula Award","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/award/show/23-nebula-award","awardedAt":883641600000,"category":"Best Novel","hasWon":false},{"__typename"